              <td style="color:#00D4AA; font-weight:600;">05</td>
              <td style="color:#F8F9FA; font-weight:500;">Six-gene chassis (Δcre-1 + Δwc-1)</td>
              <td>Requirement for 450 nm optogenetic activation in orthogonal host</td>
